    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings that house schools maintained at public expense for the education of children of a community or district as part of a free education system; generally includes elementary and high schools.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
